title: Wall Street Breakfast July 27: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Stocks rose following a set of strong earnings reports and data showing the U.S. domestic economy continuing to grow at a healthy clip, including the strongest pace for consumer spending since late 2017.
